snippet.title: CANDY CHICKEN | Chicken Popsicle | Crispy Chicken Snack Recipe Cooking in Village | Bread Recipe
snippet.description: Watch how we make CANDY CHICKEN – a fun and crispy chicken popsicle snack cooked in traditional village style! Juicy chicken is marinated with village spices, wrapped like a lollipop, coated with a crispy bread layer, and deep-fried to golden perfection. This is a must-try recipe for chicken lovers and a perfect evening snack for kids and adults alike. Don’t miss the unique cooking method and mouth-watering village flavors in every bite!

snippet.description:
Hey Guys, I’m Jonathan Amaral, better known as Jonathan Gaming, a professional BGMI esports athlete and streamer.

Since the start of my journey, my dedication to the game has been defined by precision, consistency, and an unstoppable grind. As an assaulter, I’ve built a reputation for clutch performances and high-impact gameplay, earning respect in the BGMI community. 

Through years of dedication, I’ve honed my skills, adapting to every challenge and evolving with the game. Whether in high-stakes tournaments or streaming for the gaming community, my focus remains the same - pushing the limits and delivering top-tier gameplay.

Official Red Bull Athlete 🪽
MVP of PMCO Fall Split 2019 South Asia 🏅
MVP of PUBG Mobile World League 2020 🌍

snippet.title: #Video | लाइसेंसी | Licensee | Neelkamal Singh ft. Akanksha Puri | New Bhojpuri Song | भोजपुरी गाना
snippet.description:
भोजपुरी का असली स्वैग लौट आया है! नीलकमल सिंह की दमदार आवाज़ और आकांक्षा पुरी की शानदार अदाओं के साथ पेश है लेटेस्ट धमाका "लाइसेंसी" — देखिए और सुनिए सिर्फ़ @SaregamaHumBhojpuri पर! 💥🎶

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Song Name : Licensee
Hindi - लाइसेंसी
Singer - Neelkamal Singh
Feat - Akanksha Puri
Music - Vinay Vinayak
Lyrics - Ashutosh Tiwari
Director - Paddy And Mukesh Mishra 
Choreographer - Vishnu Kumar 
Dop - Chiranjeevi 
Editor - ASY Films
Di - Rohit Singh
Arranged & Programming-Vinay Vinayak 
Mix & Master - beenuV@V2studio
Recordist - Brajesh Bagi

Lyrics:-

मुखड़ा 
हमरे जमाना चले , आगे पीछे थाना चले 
करीले इशारा तबे , सारा शामियाना चले 
बड़ी लागत डरेस तोर फैंसी बाटे 
रात बितावे साथ में चल$ 2 हाथ में बाटे करेंशी 
देही प लाइसेंसी बाटे, की गन लाइसेंसी बाटे 
जनता के दरबार लागेला , कार के बाटे एजेंसी 
देही प लाइसेंसी बाटे, की गन लाइसेंसी बाटे 

अंतरा 1 
तहार जवानी सुना ए रानी खतरा में बा 
बिलन से मिलन लिखल करेजा पतारा में बा 
   कातना लेबु त बोला मान जयबु 
   असली मरद पहचान जयबु 
   हो साझही के नाचत तू बिहान जयबु 
   पावते ही खुला उल्हा फान जयबु 
लागिला ठोके केहू ना रोके, आवे जे इमरजेंसी 
देही प लाइसेंसी बाटे, की गन लाइसेंसी बाटे 

अंतरा 2 
सुना ए कली रायफल के नली , तहरे प बा 
तोहार खजाना हमार निशाना, नजरें प बा 
    नखरा करे में गोली चली जाई 
    सारा माहौल ई बदल जाई 
    ग़दरल जवानी तोहार गल जाई 
   कोरा लेके जब नीलकमल जाई 
लेबेला माजा ऑफर बा आजा , खाली बाटे भकेंसी 
देही प लाइसेंसी बाटे, की गन लाइसेंसी बाटे 
रात बितावे साथ में चल$ 2 हाथ में बाटे करेंशी 
देही प लाइसेंसी बाटे, देही प लाइसेंसी बाटे

इस ट्रैक को सभी ओटीटी प्लेटफॉर्म्स पर सुनें।

localized.description:
भोजपुरी का असली स्वैग लौट आया है! नीलकमल सिंह की दमदार आवाज़ और आकांक्षा पुरी की शानदार अदाओं के साथ पेश है लेटेस्ट धमाका "लाइसेंसी" — देखिए और सुनिए सिर्फ़ @SaregamaHumBhojpuri पर! 💥🎶

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Song Name : Licensee
Hindi - लाइसेंसी
Singer - Neelkamal Singh
Feat - Akanksha Puri
Music - Vinay Vinayak
Lyrics - Ashutosh Tiwari
Director - Paddy And Mukesh Mishra 
Choreographer - Vishnu Kumar 
Dop - Chiranjeevi 
Editor - ASY Films
Di - Rohit Singh
Arranged & Programming-Vinay Vinayak 
Mix & Master - beenuV@V2studio
Recordist - Brajesh Bagi

Lyrics:-

मुखड़ा 
हमरे जमाना चले , आगे पीछे थाना चले 
करीले इशारा तबे , सारा शामियाना चले 
बड़ी लागत डरेस तोर फैंसी बाटे 
रात बितावे साथ में चल$ 2 हाथ में बाटे करेंशी 
देही प लाइसेंसी बाटे, की गन लाइसेंसी बाटे 
जनता के दरबार लागेला , कार के बाटे एजेंसी 
देही प लाइसेंसी बाटे, की गन लाइसेंसी बाटे 

अंतरा 1 
तहार जवानी सुना ए रानी खतरा में बा 
बिलन से मिलन लिखल करेजा पतारा में बा 
   कातना लेबु त बोला मान जयबु 
   असली मरद पहचान जयबु 
   हो साझही के नाचत तू बिहान जयबु 
   पावते ही खुला उल्हा फान जयबु 
लागिला ठोके केहू ना रोके, आवे जे इमरजेंसी 
देही प लाइसेंसी बाटे, की गन लाइसेंसी बाटे 

अंतरा 2 
सुना ए कली रायफल के नली , तहरे प बा 
तोहार खजाना हमार निशाना, नजरें प बा 
    नखरा करे में गोली चली जाई 
    सारा माहौल ई बदल जाई 
    ग़दरल जवानी तोहार गल जाई 
   कोरा लेके जब नीलकमल जाई 
लेबेला माजा ऑफर बा आजा , खाली बाटे भकेंसी 
देही प लाइसेंसी बाटे, की गन लाइसेंसी बाटे 
रात बितावे साथ में चल$ 2 हाथ में बाटे करेंशी 
देही प लाइसेंसी बाटे, देही प लाइसेंसी बाटे

इस ट्रैक को सभी ओटीटी प्लेटफॉर्म्स पर सुनें।

snippet.title: EP#01 ഒരു South Indian Family Road Trip | Preparations & Route Plan | Kochi, Kerala
snippet.description:
EP#01 ഒരു South Indian Family Road Trip | Preparations & Route Plan | Kochi, Kerala #techtraveleat #travel #familytrip 

Our next adventure begins right after INB Trip Season 2! We’re calling it the South Indian Family Trip, and it’s all about exploring the stunning landscapes, vibrant cultures, and rich flavors of Kerala, Tamil Nadu, Andhra Pradesh, Telangana, and Karnataka. In today’s video, we’re sharing all the preparations leading up to this exciting journey!

INB Trip സീസൺ 2 നു ശേഷം ഞങ്ങളുടെ പുതിയ ഫാമിലി ട്രിപ്പ് ആരംഭിക്കുകയാണ്. കേരളം, തമിഴ്നാട് ,  ആന്ധ്രാപ്രദേശ്, തെലങ്കാന, കർണാടക തുടങ്ങിയ സംസ്ഥാനങ്ങളിലെ മനോഹരമായ കാഴ്ചകളും ജീവിതങ്ങളും സംസ്‌കാരങ്ങളും രുചിവൈവിധ്യങ്ങളുമൊക്കെ ഉൾപ്പെടുത്തിക്കൊണ്ടുള്ള യാത്രയ്ക്ക് 'South Indian Family Trip' എന്നാണ് പേരിട്ടിരിക്കുന്നത്. ആ യാത്രയ്ക്കായുള്ള ഞങ്ങളുടെ ഒരുക്കങ്ങളാണ് ഇന്നത്തെ വീഡിയോയിൽ. 

00:00 Intro
01:16 Preparations for the trip
14:13 Route & Planning
15:44 Tasty Nibbles Store
21:55 Willingdon Island
24:17 Spotted Garib Rath train
25:21 Harbour Bridge, Kochi
26:05 Cochin Thirumala Devaswom Temple
29:22 Cool Bar in Mattancherry
31:37 Reached Home
33:55 Conclusion

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 4365 | 7 Apr 2025 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4365: Locked Inside
--------------------------------------------------------
As Bapuji plays a soulful tune on his harmonica remembering his dear friend, he prepares to go meet him. However, the main door is mysteriously locked from the outside. Will he find a way to get out?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4365 | 7 Apr 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Ek Date Aisi Bhi | Take A Break
snippet.description:
In Ek Date Aisi Bhi, join three friends as they set out on what they think will be the perfect romantic dates… only for everything to go hilariously wrong! 😬💔
From awkward silences and weird restaurant choices to unexpected ex-encounters and disastrous conversations, each date turns into a comedy of errors. But just when all hope seems lost, a surprising twist brings unexpected connections and a dash of real love into the mix.
Full of laughs, relatable moments, and a sweet message, this sketch proves that sometimes, even the worst dates can lead to the best stories.❤️
#EkDateAisiBhi #ComedySketch #DateGoneWrong


Produced By - Monica Prabhudesai
Creative Producer- Ravindra Sarowar

Writer - Praja Sanghmitra
Director - Satyam Phule, Prashant Kulkarni
Assistant Director - Hitan Dhaktode

Step into the world of drama, emotions, and rich Odia traditions with this gripping mega serial! 📺 Airing Monday to Saturday at 8 PM on Sidharth TV, Sindura Khela takes you on an unforgettable journey through love, family bonds, and the vibrant rituals that define our culture. 💖

With every twist, turn, and powerful performance, this show unravels the complexities of life, blending modern struggles with timeless customs. Witness the magic of marriage, devotion, and cultural pride like never before! 🌸👰

snippet.description:
#GhumHaiKisikeyPyaarMein #GHKKPM #SaasBahuAurSaazish #SBS #aditiarorasawant 

In Ghum Hai Kisikey Pyaar Meiin, the character Savi is introduced as Sai and Virat’s daughter. Savi brings a new dimension to the story as she becomes a bridge and a source of emotional complexity between her estranged parents, Sai and Virat. Her presence challenges Virat's loyalty to his family and reignites unresolved feelings between him and Sai. Rajat is another recent character who brings twists to the plot, affecting the dynamics between the main characters and creating new conflicts. Both Savi and Rajat play pivotal roles in evolving the storyline, deepening the emotional layers of the show, and introducing new conflicts that keep the characters—and viewers—on their toes.

snippet.description:
Gokuldham Society | Gada Electronics | Bonus | Financial Year

Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. Are you ready for the challenge? 

 Play now: https://gadaelectronics.page.link/dhgB  #GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame


Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Ajith சாரே Trisha மேடமுக்கு Story Narrate பண்ணிட்டார்! - Director Adhik Ravichandran | Good Bad Ugly
snippet.description:
#goodbadugly #ajith #adhikravichandran #director #interview 

Director Adhik Ravichandar's Exclusive Interview about Good Bad Ugly with Sudharshan Gandhi

In this conversation, Adhik Ravichandar discusses the success of Mark Antony and takes us through the journey of Good Bad Ugly — from ideation to post-production. He shares insights into the casting process, the film's technical team, and how he aimed to create a visual treat for Ajith's fans. Adhik also opens up about his experience of directing Ajith as a fan, as well as the memorable days spent shooting with him. Additionally, he speaks about his father and father-in-law, actor Prabhu, and shares his thoughts on Ajith's deep connection with his fans and Ajith’s Padma Bhushan award.

snippet.title: Annies Kitchen Season 3 | Episode :99 | Dhyan+Vishu+kitchen comedy=one sweet surprise!🍍😄🔥 |Amrita TV
snippet.description:
Dhyan Sreenivasan Crashes Annie’s Kitchen! 😂🍍 Vishu Special with a Sweet Twist!

This Vishu, Annie's Kitchen is filled with laughter, surprises, and sweet moments as the charming Dhyan Sreenivasan joins Annie for a festive feast! 🎉

Annie starts off the celebration by preparing a special Vishu Pradhaman, a rich and delicious payasam that sets the mood just right. But the real surprise? Dhyan walks in as a guest and stuns Annie with his unexpected visit! 😲💛

As Annie plans to treat Dhyan with a grand Vishu Sadya, she suddenly realizes she forgot to make kichadi – specifically the pineapple version she had in mind. That’s when Dhyan steps in with full spirit, offering to help her in the kitchen! 🍍👨‍🍳

Get ready for a cooking session packed with witty puns, playful banter, and heartwarming conversations as Annie and Dhyan team up to whip up the perfect Pineapple Kichadi. Along the way, Dhyan opens up about his latest projects, personal updates, and of course, adds his signature humor to every moment.

Don’t miss this fun-filled, flavor-packed Vishu Special Episode of Annie’s Kitchen! 🌼✨

"Annie's Kitchen" is a unique and exciting cookery-cum-chat show, airing every Friday at 8 PM on Amrita TV. In its second season, this delightful program is hosted by the multi-talented and charming Annie Shaji Kailas, a well-known actress in the Indian film industry. Join Annie as she whips up delicious and mouth-watering dishes in the kitchen, showcasing her culinary skills while inviting celebrity guests from the world of entertainment to join her.

                The show is divided into two engaging segments. In the first segment, watch as Annie demonstrates how to prepare a special dish, adding her personal touch and sharing handy cooking tips that will leave you craving more. In the second segment, the real fun begins! Annie sits down for a lively and entertaining chat with her celebrity guests, asking them humorous, intriguing  questions that reveal fascinating stories from their lives and careers.

                                         Annie, who is married to renowned filmmaker Shaji Kailas, brings a perfect blend of warmth and wit to every episode. Together, they have become a beloved couple in the industry, and Annie’s playful charm and insightful interviews make "Annie's Kitchen" a must-watch for viewers of all ages.

Annies Kitchen Let's Cook with Love | Friday @ 8 pm  |Amrita TV

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Money Pechu – April 7, 2025:

Global stock markets are in free fall as the US markets crash, dragging down major indices like the Dow Jones, Nasdaq, and S&P 500. The fear of a repeat Black Monday spreads like wildfire, with Hong Kong’s Hang Seng and Japan’s Nikkei plunging. In India, the pressure intensifies—petrol and diesel price hikes hit the economy hard, and Tata Motors leads the auto sector decline. Meanwhile, gold prices jump as investors rush toward safe-haven assets. Panic grips Dalal Street as Sensex and Nifty swing wildly. All eyes are now on global index heatmaps, gold rate today, and market positioning, as investors brace for volatility.

snippet.title: Superman | Sneak Peek
snippet.description:
Krypto, take us home. #Superman - Only in Theaters July 11

“Superman,” DC Studios’ first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures.  In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman who’s driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind.

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (“Twisters,” “Hollywood”) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (“The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel”) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the “X-Men” movies, “Juror #2”) as Lex Luthor.  The film also stars Edi Gathegi (“For All Mankind”), Anthony Carrigan (“Barry,” “Gotham”), Nathan Fillion (the “Guardians of the Galaxy” films, “The Suicide Squad”), Isabela Merced (“Alien Romulus”), Skyler Gisondo (“Licorice Pizza,” “Booksmart”), Sara Sampaio (“At Midnight”), María Gabriela de Faría (“The Moodys”), Wendell Pierce (“Selma,” “Tom Clancy’s Jack Ryan”), Alan Tudyk (“Andor”), Pruitt Taylor Vince (“Bird Box”) and Neva Howell (“Greedy People”).

“Superman” is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with editors William Hoy (“The Batman”), Jason Ballantine (the “IT” films, “The Flash”) and Craig Alpert (“Deadpool 2,” “Blue Beetle”).

“Superman” will be in theaters and IMAX nationwide on July 11, 2025, and internationally beginning 9 July 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

#ArrangedMarriage #VishnuUnnikrishnan #ZeroFilter 

Arranged Marriage | Season 2 | Episode 2 | Ram Weds Janani | Vishnu Unnikrishnan | Rajiththa | Divya

Welcome to Arranged Marriage, a heartfelt YouTube series that explores love found in the most unexpected way—through an arranged marriage! Follow the journey of two individuals brought together by family, tradition, and culture, who slowly discover friendship, trust, and eventually, love. Watch how their worlds collide and connect as they navigate new experiences, overcome misunderstandings, and learn what it means to truly love and respect each other.

Welcome back to Arranged Marriage Season 2! 🎉 In Episode 1, the much-awaited first night takes an unexpected turn when Janani, the newly wedded wife, gets her period at the most awkward moment. 😳 Ram, her modern-gen husband, steps up and handles the situation with care, love, and understanding. From midnight medical shop runs to comforting moments, this episode beautifully explores how real love blossoms in unexpected situations. ❤️

💑 What to Expect:
✅ Heartwarming First Night Moments
✅ Emotional Connect Between Ram & Janani
✅ Unexpected Period Twist & Care

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: FilterCopy | Reality of a NEET Aspirant | Ft. Tanya Sharma, Ruma Mondal
snippet.description:
Being a NEET aspirant in India? It’s not just about books and mock tests—it's a whole emotional rollercoaster filled with anxiety, last-minute revision, relatives asking the wrong questions, and friends who mean well but say the weirdest things. 😩📚

In this hilarious and painfully relatable FilterCopy sketch, we dive into the reality of a NEET student’s life—the pressure, the panic, and of course, the people who keep saying things like:
👉 “Beta, NEET nikaalna toh easy hai na?”
👉 “Arey Sharma ji ka beta bhi kar raha hai!”
👉 “Tumhe toh doctor banne ka passion hai na?” 😐

From group studies that turn into therapy sessions to panic before results day, this one’s for all the NEET warriors out there fighting their way through syllabus, stress, and society. 😭✊

🎯 Tag a NEET aspirant who needs a laugh break!
💬 Drop a comment and tell us the most annoying thing someone said while you were preparing. 👇

✨ Don’t forget to like, share, and subscribe to FilterCopy for more sketches that get you!

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.
